body: Hello, guys, someone has compiled a huge list, at least of 359 IP's and made them public. Scanning through this list I noticed almost every single player on the list is related to OCN. I won't post the link here because that leaves you open to massive exploitation. But if I were you I would change your IP. The simplest way to do this is to disconnect your modem and leave it off overnight and it should automatically change your IP. I don't know who made this and how they got all the IP's, but my best guess is that it's an owner of a popular scrim server, team speak or mumble room. If you think you may be on the list ask below and I'll check for you, I don't want to post the link for obvious reasons.
